[package]
name = "skytemple_rust"
version = "1.8.1"
authors = [ "Marco 'Capypara' Köpcke <hello@capypara.de>",]
edition = "2021"
repository = "https://github.com/SkyTemple/skytemple-rust"
license = "GPL-3.0-or-later"

[lib]
crate-type = [ "cdylib", "rlib",]
name = "skytemple_rust"

[features]
default = [ "strings", "compression", "image", "sir0", "kao", "map_bg", "dungeon_graphics", "misc_graphics", "md", "item_p", "waza_p", "mappa_bin", "with_pmd_wan", "script_var_table",]
strings = [ "encoding-index-singlebyte",]
compression = []
image = []
sir0 = [ "anyhow",]
kao = [ "compression", "image",]
map_bg = [ "compression", "image",]
misc_graphics = [ "image",]
dungeon_graphics = [ "image", "sir0",]
md = [ "packed_struct",]
item_p = [ "packed_struct", "sir0",]
waza_p = [ "packed_struct", "sir0", "md",]
mappa_bin = [ "packed_struct", "sir0",]
script_var_table = [ "packed_struct",]
with_pmd_wan = [ "pmd_wan", "anyhow",]
romfs = [ "nitro_fs", "memmap2", "strings",]

[dependencies]
itertools = "0.13"
log = "0.4"
bytes = "1"
num-traits = "0.2"
num-derive = "0.4"
paste = "1.0"
encoding = "0.2"
thiserror = "1"

[dependencies.skytemple_rust_macros]
path = "skytemple_rust_macros"

[dependencies.pyo3]
version = "0.22"
features = [ "extension-module",]

[dependencies.pyo3-log]
version = "0.11"

[dependencies.encoding-index-singlebyte]
version = "1"
optional = true

[dependencies.pmd_wan]
version = "5.1"
optional = true

[dependencies.anyhow]
version = "1"
optional = true

[dependencies.nitro_fs]
version = "0.2"
optional = true

[dependencies.memmap2]
version = "0.9"
optional = true

[dependencies.packed_struct]
version = "0.10"
optional = true

[target."cfg( not(target_env = \"msvc\") )".dependencies.gettext-rs]
version = "0.7"
features = [ "gettext-system",]

[package]
name = "skytemple_rust_macros"
version = "1.4.0"
authors = [ "Marco 'Capypara' Köpcke <hello@capypara.de>",]
edition = "2018"
repository = "https://github.com/SkyTemple/skytemple-rust"
license = "GPL-3.0-or-later"

[lib]
proc-macro = true

[dependencies]
quote = "1.0"

[dependencies.syn]
version = "1.0"
features = [ "full",]
